<emphasis id="B91EEA97FFD8FFCEFEDDF81DBEBAC703" bold="true" box="[380,399,2032,2053]" pageId="11" pageNumber="232">H</emphasis>
. A vertical section of a uredinium. 
<emphasis id="B91EEA97FFD8FFCEFD78F81DBDD7C703" bold="true" box="[729,738,2032,2053]" pageId="11" pageNumber="232">I</emphasis>
